  "detailed_description": "Game Features:<br>Every creak in the mansion will make you feel fear, and any paranormal event will bring anxiety and discomfort. However, the house still has electricity, even though it looks long abandoned. Light is the only thing that can calm you down, allowing you to look around and move forward. But is it really so?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fe3ac3182624830cb046c15b0ede59dd.poster.avif?t=1774445365\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fe3ac3182624830cb046c15b0ede59dd.webm?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fe3ac3182624830cb046c15b0ede59dd.mp4?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gameplay:<br>You will explore the mansion, collect useful items, and solve puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/f4884f9293bb6382194f9e534ceb4b09.poster.avif?t=1774445365\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/f4884f9293bb6382194f9e534ceb4b09.webm?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/f4884f9293bb6382194f9e534ceb4b09.mp4?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Don't expect an easy walk — danger may be lurking around every corner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/66fd7fbb5a29663fd1f1500f1d34a096.poster.avif?t=1774445365\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/66fd7fbb5a29663fd1f1500f1d34a096.webm?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/66fd7fbb5a29663fd1f1500f1d34a096.mp4?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Story:<br>You wake up on a sofa, not understanding how you got there or what this place is. After investigating the room a little, you find an article about the mysterious disappearance of an entire family. How is this related to the protagonist, or is he just a random victim? You'll need to find the answers to these and other questions. The game will have multiple endings, and the choice of which one to pursue is yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fc22b1eba5241f916e0c2373b6591224.poster.avif?t=1774445365\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fc22b1eba5241f916e0c2373b6591224.webm?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fc22b1eba5241f916e0c2373b6591224.mp4?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready to dive into the world of Echoes Of Dread and uncover all its dark secrets?",
  "about_the_game": "Game Features:<br>Every creak in the mansion will make you feel fear, and any paranormal event will bring anxiety and discomfort. However, the house still has electricity, even though it looks long abandoned. Light is the only thing that can calm you down, allowing you to look around and move forward. But is it really so?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fe3ac3182624830cb046c15b0ede59dd.poster.avif?t=1774445365\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fe3ac3182624830cb046c15b0ede59dd.webm?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fe3ac3182624830cb046c15b0ede59dd.mp4?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gameplay:<br>You will explore the mansion, collect useful items, and solve puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/f4884f9293bb6382194f9e534ceb4b09.poster.avif?t=1774445365\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/f4884f9293bb6382194f9e534ceb4b09.webm?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/f4884f9293bb6382194f9e534ceb4b09.mp4?t=1774445365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Don't expect an easy walk — danger may be lurking around every corner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/66fd7fbb5a29663fd1f1500f1d34a096.poster.avif?t=1774